::Squizzy::

The panel blinks and lights flicker.  The panel then stops 
flickering.  She lays in the pod motionless.  Then her hand clentches 
into a fist, then relaxes.  She slowly opens her eyes. She feels the 
cool air rush over her as the outside breeze picks up.  She moves her 
eyes and sees Rattrap standing there.  She looked and then closed her 
eyes.  She slowly sat up.  She then opened her eyes and looked at 
Rattrap.  She didn't speak, just looked at him with a curious 
expression on her face.
